channel.description:
[CENTER][size=20pt][b]Rυηєѕcαρє Rєвσrη[/b][/size]
Hello and welcome to my newest development called; RuneScape Reborn. That means i will remake RuneScape in the 377 version of it, with the new sprite icons because i like them you can always use a older client.. But though i will use. I've made plenty of progress in the skills, quests, city's, and so on.
[color=green][size=10pt][b]Feature's[/b][/COLOR] Dialogue's Banking Trading Shops City's Skills Combat Npc drops PK drops Emote's Npc emote's PvP PvN
[size=10pt][color=green][b]Minigame's[/b][/COLOR] TzHaar Fight Pit. TzHaar Fight Cave. Kalphite queen.
